{"tid":315403,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"官恩娜闊別樂壇近兩年 錄歌隨時復出","createTime":"2017-07-10T03:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T14:11:02.000Z","uid":14730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f33fc9ca49ab22f9f8818002b77a00cc594eb9a","tid":315403,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/115729_d4544bc490f4b82ad4b5293c4860ff69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F10%2F115729_d4544bc490f4b82ad4b5293c4860ff69.jpg&h=d8d38646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少女藝人嫁人生B後就專心相夫教子，例如謝安琪、陳慧琳及周汶錡官恩娜等等。官恩娜（Ella）也是其中之一，自 2014 年與中法混血醫生 Juan 結婚，翌年 10 月誕下混血囝囝 Gabriel 之後，就一直休息享受家庭樂，不時上載一家三口的照片，生活非常美滿溫馨。今天是 Ella 的 39 歲生日，囝囝也都 21 個月大了；最近她在 facebook 上載了在錄音室的相片，相信距離復出樂壇的日子不遠了！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2v1eljJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2v1eljJ&d=f%2BQVzLxqOPmwvy0z%2BjW7LjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=9cf310cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2v1eljJ</a>"},{"pid":"fa4507b8403ba01853c79565c465dd3d1d2897a1","tid":315403,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:06:57.000Z","msg":"官恩娜39歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb62f06b2fd157b41c3bc264d48c2f38684578ef","tid":315403,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:12:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>官恩娜39歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n38啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d039cb9f8c29e22a16a568f21b4cfd7afc5320